WEBVTT

00:24.280 --> 00:24.920
Brother.

00:31.440 --> 00:32.350
What are these?

00:34.830 --> 00:40.500
[Chief of Great Yan's Helian Tribe,
Helian Chuan]

00:36.000 --> 00:37.520
I have some good news for you.

00:37.520 --> 00:39.380
Elder Tubo of the Hongchuan Tribe

00:39.430 --> 00:41.200
wants to take you as his concubine.

00:41.200 --> 00:42.000
Look at these.

00:42.280 --> 00:44.000
These are all
the betrothal gifts they sent—

00:44.000 --> 00:46.160
a full twenty-something chests of them.

00:46.160 --> 00:46.920
Look.

00:48.240 --> 00:48.970
Look at these

00:49.070 --> 00:50.470
gold and silver jewelry.

00:53.960 --> 00:55.360
Elder Tubo also promised

00:55.920 --> 00:57.450
that after you get married,

00:57.600 --> 00:59.430
he will give us 500 horses

00:59.430 --> 01:01.000
and 200 acres of pasture.

01:01.430 --> 01:02.490
Two hundred acres.

01:03.430 --> 01:04.590
Our Helian Tribe hasn't been

01:04.590 --> 01:06.190
this glorious in a long time.

01:09.039 --> 01:10.770
Elder Tubo is over 70 years old.

01:11.590 --> 01:13.310
He also already has
three wives and concubines.

01:13.310 --> 01:14.000
Brother,

01:14.310 --> 01:15.840
you're not joking, are you?

01:16.430 --> 01:17.760
My dear sister,

01:18.590 --> 01:20.280
you should be sensible.

01:21.480 --> 01:22.150
Yes,

01:23.000 --> 01:25.430
Elder Tubo is a bit old.

01:26.510 --> 01:27.510
But you also know

01:27.950 --> 01:29.080
the Hongchuan Tribe

01:29.130 --> 01:30.710
is the most powerful

01:30.710 --> 01:32.310
of the 13 tribes in Great Yan.

01:32.660 --> 01:34.180
He is a bit old,

01:34.509 --> 01:36.840
but his wives and concubines
are not young either.

01:36.840 --> 01:38.470
Even if you marry him as a concubine now

01:38.470 --> 01:41.140
and bear him a child,

01:41.229 --> 01:42.070
in a few years,

01:42.070 --> 01:44.600
when he
and his wives and concubines are gone,

01:45.840 --> 01:47.039
this Hongchuan Tribe

01:47.280 --> 01:49.810
will become the backyard
of our Helian Tribe.

01:54.200 --> 01:56.440
Just thinking about it makes me happy.

01:57.180 --> 01:58.630
Give up on that idea.

01:59.310 --> 02:00.640
Mind your own business.

02:06.770 --> 02:08.289
Yan Xun will not marry you.

02:08.680 --> 02:09.940
For that female slave,

02:10.310 --> 02:12.840
he even stopped fighting
the war with Great Yong.

02:12.840 --> 02:14.500
You still expect to marry him?

02:14.630 --> 02:15.910
Stop daydreaming!

02:17.360 --> 02:18.240
Do you think

02:18.630 --> 02:20.190
the Hongchuan Tribe
giving you a few horses

02:20.190 --> 02:21.150
can bring back the past glory

02:21.150 --> 02:22.360
our Helian Tribe had?

02:22.480 --> 02:23.390
Let me tell you,

02:23.800 --> 02:25.400
even if you sell me to Tubo,

02:25.710 --> 02:28.030
the tribes of Great Yan
will still look down on you.

02:28.030 --> 02:29.630
You will still be the worthless prodigal

02:29.630 --> 02:30.650
mocked by those tribe elders,

02:30.650 --> 02:31.120
the—

02:33.190 --> 02:34.520
I'm warning you:

02:35.180 --> 02:37.650
Obediently marry Elder Tubo.

02:38.280 --> 02:40.310
Otherwise, I'll strangle you to death

02:40.310 --> 02:42.800
and send your corpse to him.

04:17.470 --> 04:22.600
[REBIRTH]

04:23.040 --> 04:25.530
[Episode 11]

05:15.770 --> 05:16.690
General Cheng,

05:17.270 --> 05:18.870
what else do you want from me?

05:19.190 --> 05:21.830
Do you, Lady Helian,
feel that I, Cheng Yuan, have lost power

05:21.830 --> 05:23.480
so you don't even want to see me?

05:23.480 --> 05:25.240
General Cheng, why say that?

05:25.920 --> 05:26.720
I am just

05:26.720 --> 05:28.920
an ordinary female officer in the army.

05:29.310 --> 05:31.270
What makes me capable
of being a fair-weather friend

05:31.270 --> 05:32.870
and looking down on you, General Cheng?

05:32.870 --> 05:35.159
It's just that
I can hardly protect myself now.

05:35.159 --> 05:36.680
I'm afraid it's not like before,

05:36.680 --> 05:38.680
and I can't help you with anything.

05:38.870 --> 05:39.680
What if I said

05:40.480 --> 05:41.750
I am here to help you?

05:42.409 --> 05:43.610
Would you believe it?

05:46.680 --> 05:48.600
I address you as General Cheng

05:49.120 --> 05:51.560
only because of our past alliance.

05:51.920 --> 05:53.630
You are a stray dog now,

05:53.870 --> 05:54.930
how can you help me?

05:57.090 --> 05:58.800
I am a stray dog, indeed,

05:59.600 --> 06:01.930
but I am also the one
who knows Yan Xun best.

06:07.590 --> 06:09.050
What are you trying to say?

06:13.720 --> 06:14.830
I can help you

06:15.870 --> 06:17.480
become Yan Xun's queen.

06:25.650 --> 06:26.980
What do you want me to do?

06:47.190 --> 06:47.950
Strange.

06:48.720 --> 06:50.270
In the past,
when this black eagle saw His Majesty,

06:50.270 --> 06:51.159
it would stop.

06:51.510 --> 06:53.510
Why is it acting so abnormal today?

06:55.190 --> 06:56.000
It's Chu.

06:56.790 --> 06:58.650
The black eagle brought Chu back!

07:24.870 --> 07:25.560
Chu.

07:42.360 --> 07:43.190
Your Majesty.

07:43.630 --> 07:45.690
Why did you call for this black eagle?

07:46.870 --> 07:47.720
Your Majesty,

07:48.510 --> 07:50.190
I have never seen this black eagle before,

07:50.190 --> 07:51.850
nor do I know how to call for it.

07:52.870 --> 07:54.480
It flew over

07:54.480 --> 07:55.520
while I was practicing horse riding.

07:55.520 --> 07:56.659
Maybe it was tired of flying

07:56.659 --> 07:58.520
and wanted to stop and have a rest.

08:01.950 --> 08:02.680
Is this eagle

08:02.950 --> 08:04.600
raised by Your Majesty?

08:05.680 --> 08:07.880
I see a white silk ribbon tied to its leg.

08:08.120 --> 08:10.500
This is a custom of Great Yan's herdsmen
to make a wish.

08:10.500 --> 08:13.360
Does Your Majesty
have any wish you wish to fulfill?

08:17.160 --> 08:19.240
Why do you suddenly
want to learn horse riding?

08:19.240 --> 08:21.870
Because Your Majesty
has been either hunting in the paddock

08:21.870 --> 08:24.430
or leading people
to look around for Queen Chu.

08:24.430 --> 08:25.750
I want to help Your Majesty.

08:25.750 --> 08:27.510
Even if we can't find Queen Chu,

08:27.540 --> 08:29.630
I can accompany Your Majesty to hunt

08:29.750 --> 08:30.600
and relax.

08:34.440 --> 08:36.080
I'll teach you how to ride a horse.

08:36.080 --> 08:36.870
Come with me.

10:27.550 --> 10:28.440
Chu...

10:30.840 --> 10:31.510
Chu?

10:33.270 --> 10:35.000
I asked Black Eagle to find you.

10:36.200 --> 10:36.840
Did...

10:37.480 --> 10:39.210
Did Black Eagle bring you back?

10:39.550 --> 10:40.200
Yes.

10:43.480 --> 10:44.150
Yan Xun.

10:44.770 --> 10:45.680
Look at me.

10:46.600 --> 10:47.720
I'm Chu.

10:49.000 --> 10:49.870
Chu.

10:50.440 --> 10:51.550
I miss you so much.

11:02.350 --> 11:03.110
Yan Xun.

11:04.480 --> 11:05.630
I'm Chu.

11:06.360 --> 11:07.810
I am your Chu.

11:14.710 --> 11:15.840
I missed you so much.

11:16.840 --> 11:17.640
Your Majesty.

11:18.870 --> 11:19.870
Let's drink.

11:53.480 --> 11:54.150
Chu,

11:55.180 --> 11:56.300
where did you go?

11:57.350 --> 11:58.780
I really missed you.

13:01.360 --> 13:03.490
Greetings, Princess Consort Helian.

13:05.740 --> 13:06.870
What did you call me?

13:08.000 --> 13:09.690
His Majesty has announced to Great Yan

13:09.690 --> 13:11.690
that you are appointed
as the Secondary Princess Consort of Great Yan.

13:11.690 --> 13:14.220
Congratulations, Princess Consort Helian.

13:15.710 --> 13:17.960
[Tangjing, Biantang]

13:25.750 --> 13:27.390
Is Beauty Han here?

13:28.320 --> 13:29.080
Beauty Han,

13:29.870 --> 13:31.330
I have prepared for you...

13:33.960 --> 13:35.160
Oh, it's the Empress.

13:37.240 --> 13:38.550
Greetings, Your Majesty.

13:38.550 --> 13:41.080
I must ask for your forgiveness
for one thing.

13:41.080 --> 13:42.610
I failed in raising our son,

13:42.870 --> 13:44.750
causing him to made a grave mistake.

13:44.750 --> 13:46.080
What has Ce done now?

13:54.270 --> 13:55.070
Your Majesty,

13:55.600 --> 13:57.530
Princess Fu, whom Ce brought back,

13:57.670 --> 13:59.510
is actually a criminal slave
from Great Yong,

13:59.510 --> 14:02.270
Chu Qiao,
a general of Great Yan's Xiuli Army.

14:03.360 --> 14:04.320
I originally thought

14:04.320 --> 14:06.720
Ce was just acting absurdly

14:06.790 --> 14:08.870
which was why
he had feelings for that woman.

14:08.870 --> 14:12.240
So I turned a blind eye

14:12.480 --> 14:13.670
and let him be.

14:14.000 --> 14:15.860
But at the state banquet that day,

14:16.000 --> 14:17.130
he and Chu Qiao

14:17.160 --> 14:19.280
echoed each other with King of Ximeng,

14:19.280 --> 14:20.480
colluding secretly.

14:21.780 --> 14:22.690
I suspect

14:23.600 --> 14:25.390
Ce might be secretly colluding

14:25.690 --> 14:26.810
with Ximeng.

14:30.150 --> 14:31.480
You mean

14:32.030 --> 14:35.120
Ce colluded
with General Chu Qiao of Great Yan

14:35.840 --> 14:37.870
and the King of Ximeng,

14:38.120 --> 14:38.670
right?

14:41.000 --> 14:43.060
Does Your Majesty find this amusing?

14:43.480 --> 14:44.630
I think

14:45.360 --> 14:49.080
since we Biantang
are bordering Great Yan and Great Yong,

14:50.080 --> 14:52.440
now that they are at war,

14:53.150 --> 14:56.240
no matter who wins or loses in the end,

14:56.240 --> 14:58.630
it wouldn't be a good thing for Biantang.

14:59.910 --> 15:02.320
If Ce can really make Ximeng

15:02.440 --> 15:04.510
an ally of Biantang,

15:04.600 --> 15:07.320
that would indeed relieve
one of my worries.

15:09.910 --> 15:12.030
Does Your Majesty really think so?

15:13.360 --> 15:15.080
As for this Chu Qiao,

15:15.790 --> 15:18.000
if Ce likes her, let him be.

15:18.920 --> 15:20.380
She's just a female slave.

15:20.960 --> 15:22.440
Besides, I've heard

15:22.870 --> 15:26.200
this slave once helped
Heir Apparent Yan rebel.

15:26.830 --> 15:28.070
I saw her that day too.

15:28.240 --> 15:29.370
She is quick-witted

15:29.550 --> 15:30.630
and capable.

15:30.880 --> 15:32.640
If she can be used by Ce,

15:33.270 --> 15:34.530
it's also a good thing.

15:34.550 --> 15:35.440
But this Chu Qiao's

15:35.440 --> 15:37.670
relationship with Heir Apparent Yan
is extremely complicated.

15:37.670 --> 15:39.670
I am not at ease letting her marry Ce.

15:43.750 --> 15:44.750
Isn't that

15:44.790 --> 15:47.500
exactly what you and I want?

15:47.890 --> 15:49.130
If we

15:49.320 --> 15:51.980
had not gone through
all those twists and turns,

15:52.270 --> 15:55.670
we wouldn't be in such harmony today.

15:59.150 --> 15:59.960
Someone,

16:00.280 --> 16:01.880
bring the snacks I prepared.

16:05.480 --> 16:08.110
This is your favourite pastry,

16:08.110 --> 16:09.630
Milk Poria Crisp Custard,

16:10.270 --> 16:12.670
I had the imperial kitchen
prepare for you.

16:13.150 --> 16:14.600
Come, have a taste.

16:27.570 --> 16:28.970
Thank you, Your Majesty,

16:29.600 --> 16:32.600
for remembering
my preference after all these years.

16:43.840 --> 16:44.480
Leave.

16:45.040 --> 16:45.590
Yes.

16:50.390 --> 16:51.190
Your Majesty,

16:51.670 --> 16:53.600
don't ruin your health with anger.

16:53.790 --> 16:55.320
I will definitely do my best

16:56.150 --> 16:57.240
to plan for you.

17:16.880 --> 17:17.680
Your Majesty,

17:18.000 --> 17:19.030
His Majesty not only sent people

17:19.030 --> 17:20.680
to deliver
those gold, silver and brocades,

17:20.680 --> 17:21.720
but also specifically ordered

17:21.720 --> 17:22.829
that your meals in the future

17:22.829 --> 17:24.160
will be made by the small kitchen.

17:24.160 --> 17:25.720
He said the chef in the small kitchen

17:25.720 --> 17:28.520
is best at making
the Poria Crisp Custard you love.

17:29.140 --> 17:29.970
Your Majesty!

17:32.160 --> 17:32.960
Your Majesty.

17:34.300 --> 17:35.630
What's wrong, Yan Qing?

17:39.680 --> 17:40.680
Heir Apparent...

17:42.650 --> 17:44.450
What happened to Heir Apparent?

17:44.560 --> 17:47.020
News came
from the Prince of Chang's mansion

17:47.640 --> 17:49.790
that Heir Apparent caught a plague...

17:51.310 --> 17:52.310
and passed away.

17:58.940 --> 17:59.530
What?

18:00.290 --> 18:01.900
Heir Apparent...

18:03.830 --> 18:05.240
passed away.

18:07.160 --> 18:07.960
Your Majesty!

18:08.440 --> 18:09.030
Your Majesty!

18:09.030 --> 18:09.790
Impossible.

18:10.100 --> 18:11.110
Xu is not dead.

18:11.110 --> 18:12.000
I'm going to find him.

18:12.000 --> 18:12.590
Your Majesty.

18:12.590 --> 18:13.350
I'm going to find him.

18:13.350 --> 18:14.160
Your Majesty.

18:14.160 --> 18:15.030
Let me go!

18:17.120 --> 18:17.920
Your Majesty.

18:27.790 --> 18:29.510
Xu!

18:30.270 --> 18:32.310
Your Majesty.

18:33.160 --> 18:34.200
Your Majesty!

18:34.310 --> 18:35.240
Your Majesty!

18:35.640 --> 18:36.400
Your Majesty.

18:36.400 --> 18:38.550
Xu!

18:50.070 --> 18:50.920
He who couldn't tolerate

18:50.920 --> 18:52.850
my son with Crown Prince Maocheng,

18:54.220 --> 18:55.420
so he killed Xu.

18:58.330 --> 18:59.610
He lied to me.

19:02.000 --> 19:03.510
He said he would spare Xu.

19:05.390 --> 19:07.390
Yet he used such a despicable method

19:08.510 --> 19:09.790
to kill him.

19:10.810 --> 19:11.890
It's my fault.

19:12.680 --> 19:14.160
I was incompetent.

19:15.350 --> 19:17.480
I failed to eliminate Chu Qiao for you,

19:18.200 --> 19:20.400
causing you to suffer such a grievance.

19:21.440 --> 19:23.370
Your Majesty, please don't be sad.

19:23.900 --> 19:25.380
Just punish me.

19:49.510 --> 19:50.240
Lord Zhan.

19:50.590 --> 19:52.590
Her Majesty sentenced you to 40 lashes.

19:52.590 --> 19:54.270
You should put your clothes on.

19:54.270 --> 19:55.070
Otherwise...

19:55.110 --> 19:56.980
Otherwise,
you'll be beaten to a bloody pulp.

19:56.980 --> 19:58.550
That is what I deserve.

19:59.260 --> 20:00.910
I must remember this pain,

20:01.550 --> 20:03.550
so I won't disappoint her.

20:04.550 --> 20:05.590
Continue!

20:24.070 --> 20:25.400
Last time in the palace,

20:25.400 --> 20:26.160
Her Majesty already noticed

20:26.160 --> 20:28.510
the connection between us
and King of Ximeng.

20:28.510 --> 20:29.480
Before she figures out

20:29.480 --> 20:30.550
our relationship

20:30.640 --> 20:31.880
and makes a move against us,

20:31.880 --> 20:33.240
we must act first.

20:33.270 --> 20:34.880
Yes, we must act first.

20:35.200 --> 20:36.240
I'll keep it brief.

20:36.240 --> 20:38.640
The first step is to find some people.

20:39.270 --> 20:40.110
Find some people?

20:40.110 --> 20:40.910
Let me ask you.

20:41.160 --> 20:42.440
Do you know anyone

20:42.440 --> 20:44.240
in Tangjing governor's office?

20:44.890 --> 20:45.920
Not just the governor's office.

20:45.920 --> 20:48.070
Also the Supervisory Bureau,
the Penal Bureau, and the Censorate—

20:48.070 --> 20:49.640
do you know anyone in any of these?

20:49.640 --> 20:50.270
Qiao,

20:50.510 --> 20:51.790
if I did,

20:51.880 --> 20:53.480
I wouldn't have gone to such great lengths

20:53.480 --> 20:55.160
to have you train an army in my stead.

20:55.160 --> 20:57.350
They don't need
to be high-ranking officials.

20:57.350 --> 20:58.680
Even bailiffs would do.

20:59.160 --> 21:00.110
Bailiffs?

21:00.750 --> 21:01.310
Right.

21:01.750 --> 21:02.110
You just need to

21:02.110 --> 21:03.920
have them copy the files

21:03.920 --> 21:06.580
and prisoner lists in their departments
for me.

21:35.830 --> 21:36.480
Minglu,

21:37.160 --> 21:38.200
I need your help.

21:38.680 --> 21:39.350
My help?

21:40.070 --> 21:41.130
Have you forgotten

21:41.790 --> 21:44.310
that you are the one who killed my father?

21:45.550 --> 21:47.810
What about Yan Xun, who rebelled with me?

21:50.200 --> 21:52.070
He is the Heir Apparent of Great Yan.

21:52.070 --> 21:53.400
What does that make him?

21:54.350 --> 21:55.610
If the Muhe clan hadn't

21:56.000 --> 21:57.880
tried to cover up their negligence

21:57.880 --> 22:00.340
by blaming
the soldiers defending the city,

22:01.040 --> 22:03.640
how could your father
and the soldiers of Zhenhuangcheng

22:03.640 --> 22:05.270
be sent to the guillotine?

22:06.510 --> 22:08.640
And that brutal Emperor of Great Yong—

22:08.920 --> 22:11.440
why don't you ask
why Zhenhuangcheng fell?

22:12.030 --> 22:14.400
Why don't you ask the high officials
responsible for the imperial city's safety

22:14.400 --> 22:16.160
why they killed a few imperial guards?

22:16.160 --> 22:19.720
That's because Muhe clan are trusted aides
of the Emperor of Great Yong.

22:19.720 --> 22:21.240
The lives of a few mere imperial guards

22:21.240 --> 22:24.440
mean nothing to them.

22:24.550 --> 22:27.350
They could just be killed
just to vent their anger.

22:34.750 --> 22:36.150
Then I'll kill you first,

22:36.590 --> 22:38.190
and then kill them one by one.

22:38.510 --> 22:39.920
You can't even kill me.

22:40.270 --> 22:41.420
How can you kill them?

22:41.420 --> 22:44.020
You're just saying all these
to make me give up.

22:44.350 --> 22:45.680
You're trying to tell me

22:45.860 --> 22:47.290
that in this world,

22:47.630 --> 22:48.840
I can't kill them,

22:49.880 --> 22:50.610
and my father

22:51.350 --> 22:52.790
died in vain, right?

22:54.350 --> 22:55.030
No.

22:56.240 --> 22:57.640
It's quite the contrary.

22:58.150 --> 22:59.480
I'm giving you a choice.

23:00.240 --> 23:01.030
Right now,

23:01.400 --> 23:03.530
you can either kill me with this sword,

23:03.690 --> 23:06.490
or you can use it to help me,

23:07.240 --> 23:09.310
so we can create a new world together.

23:10.110 --> 23:11.380
A new world?

23:12.480 --> 23:13.400
In this world,

23:14.750 --> 23:17.180
the lives of noble clans
are not the only ones that matter.

23:17.180 --> 23:19.970
Soldiers, commoners, and slaves—

23:20.400 --> 23:21.720
our lives and deaths

23:21.880 --> 23:23.590
should not be decided by others,

23:23.590 --> 23:25.650
but should be firmly in our own hands.

23:25.960 --> 23:27.030
I need your help.

23:27.270 --> 23:28.750
Help me change this world

23:28.750 --> 23:31.010
dominated by the royals and noble clans.

23:34.760 --> 23:37.960
Then no one will die like your father

23:38.270 --> 23:40.530
and the soldiers of Zhenhuang cheng did.

23:46.300 --> 23:48.250
If you don't believe me,

23:49.440 --> 23:50.920
you can kill me anytime.

24:06.690 --> 24:08.200
The world you talked about—

24:08.200 --> 24:09.070
is it real?

24:19.510 --> 24:20.110
Qiao.

24:20.480 --> 24:22.080
How is your selection going?

24:22.660 --> 24:23.580
I've chosen one.

24:23.580 --> 24:24.710
Come and take a look.

24:27.790 --> 24:29.400
This person's name is Wang Shi'er.

24:29.400 --> 24:30.830
He's from Pingyang County.

24:30.830 --> 24:33.160
He robbed 5 tombs of princes
from previous dynasties,

24:33.160 --> 24:35.830
and was locked up in the county prison
by the governor of Tangjing.

24:35.830 --> 24:37.270
He will be exiled to Guanbei soon.

24:37.270 --> 24:38.640
Dig from here.

24:39.030 --> 24:41.090
After digging through these 3 walls,

24:41.550 --> 24:43.880
you will reach
the back wall of the prison.

24:44.180 --> 24:45.780
Leave from here at midnight,

24:46.420 --> 24:47.830
and you can definitely escape.

24:47.830 --> 24:48.440
Let me see.

24:48.440 --> 24:48.880
Let me see too.

24:48.880 --> 24:49.350
You...

24:50.110 --> 24:51.160
Give it to me!

24:53.160 --> 24:53.890
Give it to me!

24:54.160 --> 24:54.880
Let me take a look too!

24:54.880 --> 24:57.030
This person
is proficient in civil engineering.

24:57.030 --> 24:59.070
He knows how to observe
the terrain and weather,

24:58.910 --> 25:01.260
[Grave Robber, Wang Shi'er]

24:59.590 --> 25:00.550
and is also well-versed
in the Eight Diagrams Array.

25:00.550 --> 25:01.160
Let me see!

25:01.510 --> 25:02.240
It's mine!

25:03.200 --> 25:03.720
Shoo!

25:03.720 --> 25:04.440
-Let me see!
-Don't snatch!

25:04.440 --> 25:05.000
Let me take a look!

25:05.000 --> 25:05.750
Let me see!

25:07.640 --> 25:08.350
Let me...

25:11.750 --> 25:13.640
Xiao Ran, a quack doctor.

25:14.030 --> 25:16.110
He's proficient at developing
various poisonous weeds.

25:16.110 --> 25:18.510
He was sued
for murder by a patient's family

25:18.580 --> 25:19.880
and was sentenced to death
with a reprieve.

25:19.880 --> 25:22.070
Doctor, save me.

25:35.790 --> 25:37.190
Doctor, is my disease...

25:37.770 --> 25:39.180
incurable?

25:40.510 --> 25:42.200
It's kidney deficiency.

25:42.200 --> 25:43.070
Kidney deficiency?

25:43.070 --> 25:45.240
What is kidney deficiency?

25:52.210 --> 25:56.050
[Jianghu Doctor,
Xiao Ran]

25:56.480 --> 25:57.540
He killed someone?

25:58.030 --> 25:58.960
Simply put,

25:59.110 --> 26:01.110
the patient he treated couldn't be cured.

26:01.110 --> 26:02.960
So he just fed him poison,

26:03.200 --> 26:04.370
saying that since he was
going to die anyway,

26:04.370 --> 26:06.570
he might as well test the poison for him.

26:07.400 --> 26:08.070
Qiao.

26:08.920 --> 26:10.170
Are these people you picked

26:10.170 --> 26:11.310
here to work for us

26:11.310 --> 26:12.480
or to take our lives?

26:13.750 --> 26:16.950
The Xiuli Army was also
a rebel army of Great Yan back then.

26:17.350 --> 26:20.440
Because they couldn't establish themselves
in Great Yong and Great Yan—

26:20.440 --> 26:21.810
leaving them with nowhere to go—

26:21.810 --> 26:23.410
they followed Yan Xun and me.

26:24.000 --> 26:24.920
These people

26:25.200 --> 26:26.070
are imprisoned

26:26.440 --> 26:27.480
and have skills.

26:28.000 --> 26:29.750
They were imprisoned
due to misfortune and accidents.

26:29.750 --> 26:31.920
They are far from being extremely wicked.

26:31.920 --> 26:33.850
They are just right to be used by us.

26:34.550 --> 26:35.150
All right.

26:35.590 --> 26:36.270
Qiao,

26:36.880 --> 26:38.010
you call the shoots.

26:48.200 --> 26:49.660
The one up ahead! Make way!

27:47.110 --> 27:47.750
Everyone.

27:48.110 --> 27:49.040
This restaurant

27:49.270 --> 27:51.720
originally belonged
to a friend of mine in the capital.

27:51.720 --> 27:53.070
Due to changes in his family,

27:53.070 --> 27:54.750
she was forced to leave Tangjing.

27:54.750 --> 27:55.480
Therefore,

27:55.680 --> 27:57.440
she left this restaurant to me.

27:57.960 --> 27:59.960
From now on, this restaurant

28:00.110 --> 28:03.500
will be our hiding and resting place.

28:04.270 --> 28:05.070
Friend?

28:05.680 --> 28:06.610
Female scammer.

28:07.440 --> 28:09.230
-Female scammer?
-Female scammer?

28:09.230 --> 28:12.360
Look at this dilapidated
and shabby restaurant

28:13.160 --> 28:14.440
full of holes.

28:14.470 --> 28:16.700
Do you know
how much she scammed from His Highness?

28:16.700 --> 28:17.220
This...

28:17.280 --> 28:17.840
Plus this...

28:17.840 --> 28:18.600
And this.

28:22.920 --> 28:23.590
Song Cheng.

28:23.910 --> 28:24.520
Your Highness.

28:24.520 --> 28:25.240
Come up.

28:27.480 --> 28:28.340
Your Highness.

28:30.590 --> 28:31.720
You've got a death wish?

28:31.720 --> 28:32.420
So full of nonsense.

28:32.420 --> 28:33.000
Your Highness!

28:33.000 --> 28:34.000
Full of nonsense.

28:34.790 --> 28:35.480
Get off!

28:37.680 --> 28:38.350
Everyone,

28:38.920 --> 28:42.000
this is
the current Crown Prince of Biantang.

28:42.790 --> 28:43.790
-Him?
-Him?

28:46.440 --> 28:48.110
This is the token
of my Crown Prince's Mansion.

28:48.110 --> 28:49.920
It has my father's seal on it.

28:52.720 --> 28:54.480
Take a good look at it.

28:55.260 --> 28:56.870
This is no ordinary...

29:00.030 --> 29:01.230
When did you get that?

29:01.350 --> 29:02.640
If you found out,

29:02.640 --> 29:03.750
how can I be called a master thief?

29:03.750 --> 29:04.240
I...

29:04.960 --> 29:07.220
Who knows if you're the real Crown Prince

29:08.110 --> 29:09.110
or a fake one?

29:11.790 --> 29:12.960
If you really are the Crown Prince,

29:12.960 --> 29:15.710
why don't you take us
to the Crown Prince's Mansion?

29:15.710 --> 29:17.110
Your teeth are very good.

29:17.200 --> 29:18.220
It means it's being taken care of.

29:18.220 --> 29:18.790
Scram.

29:27.830 --> 29:28.750
You know what?

29:29.450 --> 29:30.480
The belt on his body

29:30.480 --> 29:31.760
is indeed a royal item.

29:32.510 --> 29:34.130
I've seen this kind of pattern

29:34.130 --> 29:35.270
in Prince Su's tomb.

29:38.040 --> 29:39.500
Let me take a look too then.

29:45.460 --> 29:48.060
The ink pad color left on his fingers
are purple

29:48.270 --> 29:49.530
and wasn't washed off.

29:51.680 --> 29:54.640
There's a scent of pear blossom
and crabapple on his clothes.

29:54.640 --> 29:55.550
He must have passed through

29:55.550 --> 29:58.480
Shengan District and Minhe District
in the Xicheng.

29:58.580 --> 30:00.000
Besides the royal mansions, Xicheng

30:00.000 --> 30:02.530
is full of residences
of nobles and generals.

30:02.590 --> 30:04.350
He really is the Crown Prince?

30:09.880 --> 30:11.240
Your Highness!

30:11.240 --> 30:13.070
Your Highness!

30:13.070 --> 30:14.790
You are all convicted people.

30:15.200 --> 30:16.660
Whether you were wronged,

30:16.920 --> 30:18.440
made a mistake,

30:19.160 --> 30:20.550
or were forced,

30:20.790 --> 30:23.190
leaving you
with no choice but to go astray,

30:23.790 --> 30:26.270
His Highness
brought you out of prison today

30:26.830 --> 30:28.720
to give you a new choice.

30:29.510 --> 30:31.510
You can choose to serve His Highness

30:31.920 --> 30:34.400
and live a new life under a new identity.

30:52.230 --> 30:54.650
♪ Facing the wind, I tread through frost ♪

30:54.700 --> 30:58.070
♪ Measuring rivers and hills,
hooves rise light ♪

30:58.750 --> 31:00.870
♪ The horizon lies far ahead ♪

31:01.070 --> 31:03.440
♪ Swaying gently ♪

31:05.500 --> 31:07.720
♪ Through pine mists, past 1,000 hills ♪

31:07.750 --> 31:11.130
♪ Wrapped in the vast moonlight ♪

31:12.010 --> 31:14.730
♪ Having drunk the surging waves ♪

31:14.750 --> 31:17.390
♪ I care not how far the road ♪

31:19.070 --> 31:21.470
♪ When I was young,
I penned down a long chapter ♪

31:21.830 --> 31:24.890
♪ I wrote poems
praising the prosperous world ♪

31:25.050 --> 31:28.210
♪ The wind was not yet full,
the moon not yet round ♪

31:28.240 --> 31:32.270
♪ Rushing me to charge forward ♪

31:33.240 --> 31:34.840
♪ Strong wine to the wild plains ♪

31:34.870 --> 31:36.680
♪ Beyond the pass,
sand blows like arrows ♪

31:36.700 --> 31:38.090
♪ I ride and whip my steed ♪

31:38.120 --> 31:39.940
♪ Chasing 10,000 miles of cloud and mist ♪

31:39.960 --> 31:41.410
♪ Mountains and rivers fade behind ♪

31:41.440 --> 31:43.440
♪ The wind crowns me ♪

31:43.460 --> 31:46.410
♪ Your eyes glow with flame ♪

31:46.440 --> 31:48.260
♪ Strong wind breaks the lute strings ♪

31:48.280 --> 31:50.120
♪ Playing for 5,000 years ♪

31:50.240 --> 31:51.740
♪ I ride my horse toward the south ♪

31:51.770 --> 31:53.530
♪ Endless spring beneath my hooves ♪

31:53.550 --> 31:54.950
♪ Hoofbeats fade away ♪

31:55.020 --> 31:56.590
♪ Rolling over peaks and ridges ♪

31:56.640 --> 31:59.850
♪ A single neigh echoes
between heaven and earth ♪

31:59.880 --> 32:01.820
♪ Treading on the clear wind ♪

32:03.080 --> 32:05.150
♪ The realm unfolds like a scroll ♪

32:06.270 --> 32:08.270
♪ Chasing the bright moon ♪

32:09.710 --> 32:12.870
♪ My spirit swallows
mountains and rivers ♪

32:27.000 --> 32:27.930
What's going on?

32:28.310 --> 32:29.070
Princess,

32:29.560 --> 32:31.510
there seems to be a lantern festival
on Tianque Street tonight.

32:31.510 --> 32:33.030
There are pedestrians everywhere ahead.

32:33.030 --> 32:36.430
I'm afraid we have to take a detour
to return to the residence.

33:02.080 --> 33:05.700
♪ The dust in the world ♪

33:05.960 --> 33:09.430
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

33:10.400 --> 33:13.200
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

33:13.860 --> 33:15.200
♪ And not be scared? ♪

33:15.320 --> 33:17.340
♪ A slight ripple ♪

33:17.610 --> 33:21.200
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

33:21.480 --> 33:24.850
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

33:25.610 --> 33:28.590
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

33:29.290 --> 33:32.670
♪ Let it be ♪

33:33.750 --> 33:37.180
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

33:37.650 --> 33:40.670
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

33:41.040 --> 33:42.680
♪ Go weaving ♪

33:43.000 --> 33:47.960
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

33:48.640 --> 33:51.180
♪ We face ♪

33:51.210 --> 33:55.060
♪ The heavy thunderstorm together ♪

33:56.830 --> 33:57.830
I have roughly figured out

33:57.830 --> 33:59.400
the locations within Tangjingcheng.

33:59.400 --> 34:01.000
Centered around the palace,

34:01.110 --> 34:03.160
the Six Ministries
are located in the southeast

34:03.160 --> 34:04.440
and southwest corners.

34:04.440 --> 34:06.550
And the official of the Ministry of Works,
Zhang Qingzhao, whom we are looking for,

34:06.550 --> 34:07.550
is not among the 6.

34:07.920 --> 34:10.320
He belongs to
the secret Manufacturing Bureau.

34:10.320 --> 34:12.190
The Manufacturing Bureau is responsible
for palace reconstruction,

34:12.190 --> 34:13.320
Tangjing's city defense,

34:13.320 --> 34:15.760
and the waterways
connecting Biantang with other countries.

34:15.760 --> 34:18.080
They control all the open and secret files
of Biantang's city defense.

34:18.080 --> 34:19.280
It's a confidential office.

34:19.280 --> 34:20.880
As for Zhang Qingzhao himself,

34:20.880 --> 34:23.000
it's difficult for an outsider
to find out about his whereabouts.

34:23.000 --> 34:24.330
Then where do we start?

34:24.960 --> 34:26.889
We can only use the dumbest method.

34:27.120 --> 34:28.250
The dumbest method?

34:37.480 --> 34:38.360
Princess Fu!

34:39.480 --> 34:40.190
Princess Fu.

34:40.190 --> 34:42.320
His Highness and I
specially prepared this for you.

34:42.320 --> 34:43.230
Do you like it?

34:43.510 --> 34:45.440
Zi Ming prepared all these for you.

34:45.630 --> 34:47.830
She wanted to celebrate your birthday.

34:49.070 --> 34:51.630
Today is Princess Fu's birthday.

34:55.630 --> 34:56.440
No need.

34:56.889 --> 34:59.090
I'm not used to celebrating birthdays.

34:59.230 --> 34:59.900
Princess Fu,

34:59.900 --> 35:01.900
my family declined when I was young,

35:02.000 --> 35:03.200
and I was sold as a slave.

35:03.200 --> 35:04.760
It's all thanks to His Highness
for saving me,

35:04.760 --> 35:06.090
and you for taking me in.

35:06.400 --> 35:07.400
I am grateful,

35:07.400 --> 35:10.060
so I sincerely want to
celebrate your birthday.

35:12.340 --> 35:13.070
Princess Fu,

35:13.150 --> 35:14.550
take a look at this first.

35:18.840 --> 35:20.000
This pair of agate bracelets

35:20.000 --> 35:21.590
symbolizes two flowers
growing on one stalk.

35:21.590 --> 35:23.360
It means I wish you and His Highness

35:23.360 --> 35:25.220
a long and lasting relationship.

35:25.970 --> 35:26.740
No need.

35:26.920 --> 35:29.050
I don't usually like wearing jewelry.

35:30.280 --> 35:31.030
Let's eat.

35:36.000 --> 35:36.600
Princess,

35:36.740 --> 35:37.930
this is Hong River fish.

35:37.930 --> 35:38.850
It's very rare.

35:42.080 --> 35:43.750
Do you not like this fish either?

35:43.750 --> 35:44.270
I...

35:44.690 --> 35:45.890
I'm choking on a bone.

36:01.030 --> 36:03.320
Are you surprised? Are you shocked?

36:03.340 --> 36:04.820
What are you trying to do?

36:04.880 --> 36:05.510
Fu.

36:06.480 --> 36:08.740
Zi Ming was being ridiculous last night.

36:08.920 --> 36:10.670
You've also been going out early
and coming back late these days.

36:10.670 --> 36:11.930
You must be very tired.

36:12.440 --> 36:15.440
So I specially designed
this house-carriage for you.

36:15.960 --> 36:18.150
House-carriage?

36:22.440 --> 36:23.960
Please get on, Fu,

36:24.190 --> 36:25.520
to the house-carriage.

36:27.590 --> 36:28.230
Qiao.

36:29.150 --> 36:29.840
Look.

36:30.480 --> 36:31.880
In this house-carriage,

36:32.280 --> 36:34.230
you can not only rest and drink tea,

36:34.850 --> 36:37.250
but also stay overnight
and use the toilet.

36:38.630 --> 36:39.850
This small icebox

36:39.950 --> 36:40.960
can store some guiling jelly

36:40.960 --> 36:43.030
and rose drink in summer.

36:43.280 --> 36:45.630
They're for you to stay rested
and refresh yourself

36:45.630 --> 36:46.510
on the road.

36:47.000 --> 36:47.630
How is it?

36:48.760 --> 36:49.510
Not bad.

36:52.000 --> 36:53.190
Thank you,

36:53.190 --> 36:55.150
our dashing

36:55.150 --> 36:56.360
and charming Crown Prince,

36:56.360 --> 36:57.110
Handsome Li.

36:57.760 --> 37:00.230
It's just a small token of my regard.
Don't mention it.

37:00.230 --> 37:01.560
Oh, right, Handsome Li.

37:01.760 --> 37:03.420
I have something to ask of you.

37:03.760 --> 37:04.360
Go ahead.

37:04.470 --> 37:06.280
You are going to be an envoy
in one the coming days

37:06.280 --> 37:07.280
accompanying Zhuge Yue?

37:07.280 --> 37:08.070
Yes, Qiao.

37:08.230 --> 37:09.030
What's wrong?

37:10.880 --> 37:13.080
Based on my understanding of Zhuge Yue,

37:13.400 --> 37:15.760
his visit to Biantang this time
is not simple.

37:15.760 --> 37:17.360
He must have his own purpose.

37:17.590 --> 37:18.760
Whether it's for Ximeng

37:18.760 --> 37:20.000
or for himself—

37:20.510 --> 37:21.960
you must be careful.

37:24.480 --> 37:24.880
Also,

37:24.820 --> 37:27.160
[Tangjing, Biantang]

37:25.510 --> 37:26.960
tell me everywhere he goes to

37:26.960 --> 37:27.820
those few days.

37:28.000 --> 37:29.920
This is the main street of Tangjing.

37:29.920 --> 37:31.520
It's called Tianque Street.

37:31.590 --> 37:33.480
There are 64 districts in Tangjing.

37:33.480 --> 37:34.880
Tianque Street and the palace

37:34.880 --> 37:36.110
splits it into half.

37:36.400 --> 37:38.320
There are 32 workshops on each side.

37:38.320 --> 37:40.070
There are two markets
both in the east and west.

37:40.070 --> 37:42.200
The east market is mostly restaurants

37:42.360 --> 37:43.280
and theaters.

37:44.050 --> 37:46.390
The west market sells silk, gold, jade,

37:46.670 --> 37:47.800
spices, herbs,

37:47.960 --> 37:49.400
and even rare animals.

37:51.190 --> 37:52.920
There are 4 canals

37:53.110 --> 37:54.170
in Tangjingcheng.

37:54.590 --> 37:57.590
Among them, Furong Canal
leads to the southeast of the city,

37:57.590 --> 38:00.250
which is the Imperial Garden
built by my father.

38:00.590 --> 38:02.590
Jinshui River leads to the northwest,

38:02.590 --> 38:05.520
where 12 ancient temples
are located in the suburbs.

38:05.920 --> 38:07.550
Don't forget the purpose of this trip.

38:07.550 --> 38:09.350
We are not here for sightseeing.

38:10.150 --> 38:11.320
I can't do this anymore.

38:11.320 --> 38:12.000
Zhuge—

38:13.110 --> 38:13.970
King of Ximeng,

38:14.150 --> 38:15.920
we've been walking for a few days.

38:15.920 --> 38:17.480
You've visited everywhere in Biantang,

38:17.480 --> 38:19.400
from government offices
to brothels and theaters.

38:19.400 --> 38:20.590
Haven't you seen enough?

38:20.590 --> 38:21.360
Besides,

38:21.360 --> 38:23.150
what's so good about watchtowers?

38:23.150 --> 38:24.920
This is already the third one
we've climbed today.

38:24.920 --> 38:25.760
Your Highness,

38:25.760 --> 38:27.800
how many watchtowers like this are there

38:27.800 --> 38:28.960
in Tangjingcheng in total?

38:28.960 --> 38:29.800
There are...

38:32.360 --> 38:33.110
30 in total.

38:33.740 --> 38:34.600
Your Highness,

38:34.900 --> 38:35.860
it's 130.

38:36.710 --> 38:38.230
You call this 130?

38:38.230 --> 38:39.400
Isn't this 130?

38:40.370 --> 38:40.890
I...

38:42.960 --> 38:43.960
130.

38:43.960 --> 38:45.560
Let's go look at the next one.

39:05.840 --> 39:09.280
The audience has assembled.
The show begins.

39:09.400 --> 39:10.030
Xing'er,

39:10.560 --> 39:12.290
I know you have many questions,

39:12.400 --> 39:14.000
and I owe you some explanations.

39:14.000 --> 39:15.330
I don't know why,

39:15.920 --> 39:17.230
but my feelings for him

39:17.730 --> 39:19.380
make me hurt so much.

39:23.480 --> 39:24.550
You mean

39:24.840 --> 39:27.170
these stitches might be some kind of code?

39:27.360 --> 39:28.400
I asked you to meet here

39:28.400 --> 39:29.800
to discuss a cooperation with you.
